    <item>
      <title>中东供应风险主导油价连续第三天上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价连续第三天上涨，因为交易商评估了中东的供应风险，预计以色列将在本周早些时候对伊朗发动导弹袭击后对伊朗进行报复性打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-3</guid>
